   SAN FRANCISCO -- BEI Electronics Inc. said it agreed to
pay $22 million for four divisions of Systron Donner Corp., a
Concord-based unit of Britain's Thorn EMI PLC.
   The Systron divisions will provide technology to bolster
BEI's business of selling sensors for applications in such
