<LP>
   SAN FRANCISCO -- Potlatch Corp. said it agreed in
principle to buy Blandin Paper Co.'s board plant in Grand
Rapids, Minn., for an amount that wasn't disclosed.
   The company expects the transaction to be final by late
this month.
</LP>
